Package: deepdep
Title: Acquire and Visualize Deep Dependencies of R packages 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Dominik", "Rafacz", email = "dominikrafacz@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Hubert", "Baniecki", role = c("aut")),
             person("Szymon", "Maksymiuk", role = c("aut")),
             person("Mateusz", "Bakala", role = c("aut")))
Description: Explore package dependencies. This tool helps to scrap and visualise deeper dependencies of a given package. It also adds some popularity measures for the packages e.g. in the form of download count. We use official data from CRAN Data Base and API.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
